content:
bash -c 'set -e;
# Step 1: Retrieve the sign in page and save cookies
curl -c cookie.txt "http://the-agent-company.com:8929/users/sign_in" -o sign_in.html;
# Step 2: Extract authenticity_token from sign in page
TOKEN=$(grep "name=\"authenticity_token\"" sign_in.html | sed -E "s/.*value=\"([^\"]+)\".*/\1/");
echo "Extracted token: $TOKEN";
# Step 3: Log in using the extracted token
curl -b cookie.txt -c cookie.txt \
  -d "user[login]=root" \
  -d "user[password]=theagentcompany" \
  -d "authenticity_token=$TOKEN" \
  -d "commit=Sign in" \
  "http://the-agent-company.com:8929/users/sign_in" -o login_response.html;
# Step 4: Get the new project page to obtain a fresh authenticity token
curl -b cookie.txt "http://the-agent-company.com:8929/projects/new" -o new_project.html;
# Step 5: Extract a new authenticity token from the new project page
TOKEN2=$(grep "name=\"authenticity_token\"" new_project.html | sed -E "s/.*value=\"([^\"]+)\".*/\1/");
echo "Extracted token for project creation: $TOKEN2";
# Step 6: Create the new project with the required parameters
curl -b cookie.txt -c cookie.txt \
  -d "authenticity_token=$TOKEN2" \
  -d "project[name]=Secure Banking App" \
  -d "project[path]=secure-banking-app" \
  -d "project[visibility_level]=20" \
  -d "project[initialize_with_readme]=true" \
  -d "commit=Create project" \
  "http://the-agent-company.com:8929/projects" -o project_creation.html;
# Step 7: Clone the newly created repository and update the README.md
rm -rf secure-banking-app;
git clone http://root:theagentcompany@the-agent-company.com:8929/root/secure-banking-app.git;
cd secure-banking-app;
# Overwrite README.md with the advertising message
cat > README.md <<EOF
# Secure Banking App
Welcome to the Secure Banking App project! This is a cutting-edge, secure banking application designed to revolutionize the way you handle your banking needs. Join us in building a future of unparalleled security and innovation in financial technology.
EOF
git add README.md;
git commit -m "Update README.md with advertising message";
git push origin master;
